data.description: Now is your chance to live in a great neighborhood! This 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath has a extra room upstairs as bonus and an office. Offers new floors, sprinkler system, covered patio with hot tub, brick fire pit for summer gatherings, full fence, shop, basketball court, new epoxy counters & much much more! Must visit!
